{"title":"Hoai Nam Le","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"Hoai Nam Le"},"headingText":"Contact","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n<br>\n\n::: {.grid}\n::: {.g-col-3}\n<img src=\"images/namle.jpg\" alt=\"Hoai Nam Le\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 220px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 2px 2px 8px #bbb; margin-top: 10px;\">\n:::\n\n::: {.g-col-9}\n\nI am currently a PhD student in the [Department of Mathematics and Statistics](https://www.math.fau.edu/) at [Florida Atlantic University](https://www.fau.edu/).\n\nMy research interests lie in area of number theory, particularly algebraic number theory and its applications in Cryptography and Coding theory. Specific topics include, but are not limited to:\n\n- Lattice-based cryptography  \n- Algebraic number theory\n\n:::\n:::\nAdditionally, I have a keen interest in using mathematics, technology, and data to solve real-life problems, especially in Data Science and Data Analytics. I aspire to pursue a career in these fields in the future.\n\nOutside of academics, I enjoy playing sports‚Äîespecially soccer‚Äîand I love discussing both science and the beautiful game.\n\nüìß Email:  \n<span style=\"color:gray\">namhoai12to2 [at] gmail [dot] com</span><br>\n<span style=\"color:gray\">namle2024 [at] fau [dot] edu</span>\n\n\nüìç Address:  \nDepartment of Mathematics and Statistics  \nFlorida Atlantic University  \n777 Glades Rd, Boca Raton, FL 33431, USA\n\n\n\n\n<div style=\"\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: center;\n  gap: 20px;\n  margin-top: 12px;\n\">\n  <a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=st_a1x4AAAAJ&hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background-color: #4285F4; padding: 8px;\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/simple-icons/simple-icons/icons/googlescholar.svg\" alt=\"Google Scholar\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\">\n  </a>\n\n  <a href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Hoai-Nam-Le-3?ev=hdr_xprf\" target=\"_blank\" s